      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, dents, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
