    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation. It's a great opportunity to own a quality vehicle at a very accessible price point!",
