    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project car. The engine currently runs roughly and will require significant diagnostic work and repairs to be roadworthy, and the transmission shifts harshly. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with significant paint peeling and several large dents. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is for parts or restoration.",
      "price": 6500.0,
